<h2>Patient query needs a manual response</h2>

<p>The AI receptionist has flagged a WhatsApp conversation for human follow-up.</p>

<table>
  <tr><td><strong>Patient:</strong></td><td><%= @patient_name %></td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Phone:</strong></td><td><%= @patient_phone %></td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Reason:</strong></td><td><%= @reason %></td></tr>
</table>

<% if @conversation_url.present? %>
  <p><a href="<%= @conversation_url %>">Open the conversation in the dashboard</a></p>
<% end %>

<p>Replying via the dashboard automatically pauses the AI for 4 hours on this conversation so it does not contradict your reply.</p>

<hr>
<p style="font-size: 0.85em; color: #888;">Sent by the Le Roux Dental AI Receptionist · <%= PracticeConfig.practice[:name] %></p>
